_sText:
So this map didn't take near as long as I thought it was going to. Was planning on it being like a month long project but it only took about a week.

The gameplay style is a lot different from my normal style. Its more of a tradition bhop map than my normal surf hybrid maps. The map is about 2 minutes on a casual run but there is  plenty of skips and optimizations to be made.

There is one small bonus. Just make sure you put the start zone within the corridor or it may be breakable.
